	   <tr><td colspan=2>amazing weapon picked wun up the other day and i (warrior) use it in preference to a lot of other toys.<br><br>at 32/36 when you use your mighty strikin discipline, with 255 str and 232 skill inpiercing you can do a @#%^load of crips up to around the mid 400's.&nbsp;&nbsp;I can hit harder by a negligable amount using my truncheon of doom 33/44 but obviously nowhere near as speedily )<br><br><br>this weapon is pure power and rather amazing to boot, we got it using one group and im nearly 100% certain it came off a chetari warrior/dominator kind of mob not a dust or chelaki etc however that dont mean it wont :)<br><br>just go to the ramp down into the chetari caves and stop short of the beetle trap and pull theres a wanderer there every 28 mins or so and it can be nasty to have trap wanderer and pull on you as a single group at once since the enchanters have a tough time using their normal mezz's, use short duration mezz to stick it first off and then go with what you know shamans a must and our shaman found that using lower lvl spells sometimes helped (i think he was sticking em with like ridiculous wimpy poison bolt @#%^ at the end but it was sticking every time and every bit helps).We picked up this weapon a 30/35 claydmore a 32/40 brawl stick(not sure on stats) and a 30/35 war lance.  Took about 4 hours of camping and included 2 cr's due to unfavourable conditions(more then 3 unmezzable mobs in camp at any one time).<br><br><br>thanks go to me bruddah cailen  the enchanter masheen), who won the roll on this monster then passed it on to me a lil later in the day heh.  Me being a warrior was creaming about this baby and he did a mighty deed by lettin me in on the action, afterwe'd nocked keleren'dar on his ass in cobalt scar.<br><br>Bushka Everluvin<br>ogure warrior to da stars.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
